name: Style du Jour
overview: Style du Jour is a company dedicated to personal style. It is a place for people to organize and execute their own sense of what is fashion. Whether you are a student or a working professional, they know that you have your own look. They want you to show them what that look is. Style du Jour is perfect for the person who is looking to express themselves or is too busy to fuss with an unorganized closet. They will help you organize your wardrobe online so you have an easy, manageable, and fun way to put your look together. Don’t know what to wear? That’s fine, they can help you. Ask the your friends, ask the community, or let their site suggest what works. Know what you like? they can still help! When creating outfits they will give suggestions of things to purchase that fit your style.
